18
00:00:12,415 --> 00:00:15,415
http://hiqve.com/

19
00:00:17,439 --> 00:00:20,901
<i>As the war between the Republic
and the Separatists intensifies,</i>

20
00:00:20,984 --> 00:00:23,236
<i>many are driven
from their home planets,</i>

21
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:26,781
<i>and it is up to Senator Amidala
to secure aid for them.</i>

22
00:00:27,282 --> 00:00:31,369
<i>All eyes turn to the Banking Clan
and the planet Scipio.</i>

23
00:00:31,453 --> 00:00:35,040
<i>In an effort to remain independent
from the Republic and the Separatists,</i>

24
00:00:35,123 --> 00:00:36,833
<i>all operations are divided</i>

25
00:00:36,917 --> 00:00:39,711
<i>and money transactions
are performed in a neutral zone</i>

26
00:00:39,794 --> 00:00:41,713
<i>surrounding the main vault.</i>

27
00:00:41,796 --> 00:00:46,426
<i>For operations to continue,
there must be no war on Scipio.</i>

28
00:00:46,509 --> 00:00:49,304
<i>However, worry about the stability
of the Banking Clan</i>

29
00:00:49,429 --> 00:00:50,931
<i>is brewing within the Republic</i>

30
00:00:51,014 --> 00:00:54,893
<i>as the wellspring of money
may be in jeopardy.</i>

31
00:00:57,229 --> 00:00:59,689
Welcome to Scipio, Senator.

32
00:00:59,773 --> 00:01:01,316
If you will follow me,

33
00:01:01,399 --> 00:01:04,444
we will be traveling
into the neutral zone.

34
00:01:21,378 --> 00:01:25,590
I am afraid your guards
will have to wait outside.

35
00:01:25,674 --> 00:01:27,175
Of course.

36
00:02:13,221 --> 00:02:17,309
<i>As Council of Five,
we are honored but surprised</i>

37
00:02:17,392 --> 00:02:21,396
<i>that you have traveled all this way
for a mere bank transfer.</i>

38
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:24,316
A transfer that has
not been forthcoming.

39
00:02:24,399 --> 00:02:28,486
By request of the Supreme Chancellor,
I am here to expedite matters.

40
00:02:28,570 --> 00:02:29,738
<i>Of course.</i>

41
00:02:29,821 --> 00:02:33,825
<i>We would merely request that you
meet with our special representative</i>

42
00:02:33,908 --> 00:02:38,246
<i>who will go over the terms
and conditions of your loan.</i>

43
00:02:46,463 --> 00:02:48,173
Senator Amidala.

44
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,008
Clovis.

45
00:02:50,091 --> 00:02:52,427
<i>You two know one another?</i>

46
00:02:52,844 --> 00:02:54,429
Sir, I was assured

47
00:02:54,512 --> 00:02:57,974
that this transaction would be free
of prejudice and partisan allegiance.

48
00:02:58,058 --> 00:03:02,145
This man is a known Separatist
and traitor to the Republic.

49
00:03:02,228 --> 00:03:04,606
-Padmé...
<i>-I can assure you</i>

50
00:03:04,689 --> 00:03:08,276
<i>Rush Clovis is our most trusted
and best negotiator.</i>

51
00:03:08,777 --> 00:03:10,403
I am sorry, gentlemen.

52
00:03:10,487 --> 00:03:14,157
But I insist that this man be removed
from these negotiations.

53
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:17,452
Until then, we have nothing further
to discuss.

54
00:03:39,974 --> 00:03:43,311
Milady no longer requires
your assistance this evening.

55
00:03:43,395 --> 00:03:44,813
Thank you.

56
00:03:50,026 --> 00:03:51,653
Milady, watch out!

57
00:03:51,986 --> 00:03:54,656
I would stop right there if I were you.

58
00:03:56,116 --> 00:03:58,618
How did you get a blaster
into the neutral zone?

59
00:03:58,701 --> 00:04:00,161
We're resourceful.

60
00:04:00,245 --> 00:04:03,248
Now, why are you breaking in
to my quarters?

61
00:04:03,331 --> 00:04:06,709
Padmé, you don't understand
what is going on here.

62
00:04:06,793 --> 00:04:07,836
I need your help.

63
00:04:08,086 --> 00:04:10,588
Last time you needed my help,
I ended up poisoned,

64
00:04:10,672 --> 00:04:11,923
and you did nothing.

65
00:04:12,006 --> 00:04:15,343
That's not true.
You stole data files from me.

66
00:04:15,427 --> 00:04:18,096
That revealed the location
of a Separatists' droid factory

67
00:04:18,179 --> 00:04:19,806
sponsored by you!

68
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:23,560
Look, it's not safe. We can't talk here.

69
00:04:27,856 --> 00:04:29,566
Senator, I really don't think...

70
00:04:29,649 --> 00:04:32,861
It's all right.
I want to hear what he has to say.

71
00:04:48,376 --> 00:04:52,255
The simple fact is the economics
of this war are not adding up.

72
00:04:52,338 --> 00:04:53,965
You're here for a bank transfer,

73
00:04:54,048 --> 00:04:56,968
but I can assure you
there is no money in the bank.

74
00:04:57,051 --> 00:04:58,636
That's absurd.

75
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,722
They were ready
to give me the funds today.

76
00:05:01,723 --> 00:05:04,476
They will give you
your first installment, yes.

77
00:05:04,559 --> 00:05:06,895
But they're robbing one side
to save the other.

78
00:05:06,978 --> 00:05:09,647
The entire Banking Clan
is on the verge of collapse.

79
00:05:09,731 --> 00:05:12,358
Collapse? Where is the evidence?

80
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:14,569
In the vault.
The accounts are sealed there,

81
00:05:14,652 --> 00:05:17,822
and no one is allowed to see them
besides the Core Five.

82
00:05:18,323 --> 00:05:19,741
Convenient.

83
00:05:27,081 --> 00:05:30,335
Well, now that you're here,
you must put pressure on them.

84
00:05:30,418 --> 00:05:32,712
And do what exactly?

85
00:05:32,795 --> 00:05:35,381
Help me gain access to the vault.

86
00:05:35,465 --> 00:05:39,219
You're insane to think
I would ever trust you.

87
00:05:39,302 --> 00:05:41,804
I'm sorry, but I cannot help you.

88
00:05:46,142 --> 00:05:47,810
Take your hands off me!

89
00:05:50,980 --> 00:05:52,941
I've risked everything to tell you this.

90
00:05:53,024 --> 00:05:55,235
Don't you see they're trying to kill me
because of what I know?

91
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:06,454
Please believe me.
Our past must count for something.

92
00:06:06,538 --> 00:06:09,457
I can't stay here. Think about what I ask.

93
00:06:32,981 --> 00:06:34,941
<i>If what you are saying is true,</i>

94
00:06:35,275 --> 00:06:40,196
<i>then this information Clovis is offering
is vital to our security.</i>

95
00:06:41,155 --> 00:06:45,785
<i>I need you to be very clear
in this matter for the Republic.</i>

96
00:06:46,536 --> 00:06:48,454
<i>Is he telling the truth?</i>

97
00:06:49,163 --> 00:06:51,124
Yes. I'm sure.

98
00:06:51,207 --> 00:06:53,585
<i>Perhaps then, in this scenario,</i>

99
00:06:53,668 --> 00:06:57,630
<i>it would be best for you
to trust an old friend</i>

100
00:06:57,714 --> 00:06:59,799
<i>and do what he suggests.</i>

101
00:07:21,487 --> 00:07:25,325
I have decided to accept Clovis
as the representative of this transaction

102
00:07:25,408 --> 00:07:27,285
as long as I can go into the vault

103
00:07:27,368 --> 00:07:30,204
and accompany the funds
throughout the entire process.

104
00:07:30,538 --> 00:07:34,334
<i>No outsider
is ever allowed into the vaults.</i>

105
00:07:34,417 --> 00:07:37,462
I come with the authority
of the Supreme Chancellor.

106
00:07:37,545 --> 00:07:38,963
If you have something to hide,

107
00:07:39,047 --> 00:07:41,132
then that is something
we should discuss.

108
00:07:41,215 --> 00:07:42,383
Hide?

109
00:07:42,467 --> 00:07:45,303
I think considering
last night's attack on the Senator,

110
00:07:45,386 --> 00:07:49,307
it is only fair that we are transparent
and agree to these terms.

111
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:50,892
What harm will come of it?

112
00:07:55,647 --> 00:07:58,733
The vault will be open
first thing in the morning.

113
00:07:58,816 --> 00:08:01,361
Please make sure
you are here, Senator.

114
00:08:19,295 --> 00:08:21,881
Where exactly are we, Clovis?

115
00:08:21,964 --> 00:08:24,133
This is my personal residence.

116
00:08:24,217 --> 00:08:27,553
A bit remote,
but we'll have more privacy here.

117
00:08:37,438 --> 00:08:41,025
Once I detonate the charge here
at the main power source,

118
00:08:41,109 --> 00:08:43,569
the vault will go
into immediate shutdown.

119
00:08:48,282 --> 00:08:50,243
No one will get in or out.

120
00:08:50,326 --> 00:08:51,786
This will give you very little time

121
00:08:51,869 --> 00:08:55,540
before the emergency generator cycles
and takes over.

122
00:08:56,290 --> 00:08:58,209
You'll then use this
to locate the exact files

123
00:08:58,292 --> 00:09:01,379
and download them
from the mainframe.

124
00:09:03,005 --> 00:09:05,466
The vault is one
of the most secure in the galaxy.

125
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:08,261
But it was designed to keep people out.

126
00:09:09,387 --> 00:09:11,848
Once you're inside,
and the power is down,

127
00:09:11,931 --> 00:09:13,808
there is little they can do.

128
00:09:20,273 --> 00:09:21,983
You make it sound so easy.

129
00:09:22,066 --> 00:09:25,486
If you don't mind, Senator,
I will retire for the night.

130
00:09:25,570 --> 00:09:27,739
Of course, Teckla.

131
00:09:27,822 --> 00:09:30,408
The information we get tomorrow
will go a long way

132
00:09:30,491 --> 00:09:33,453
to expose, perhaps,
the real criminals behind this war.

133
00:09:33,703 --> 00:09:37,248
These are war profiteers.
I've exposed that before.

134
00:09:37,331 --> 00:09:38,833
Nobody cares.

135
00:09:38,916 --> 00:09:41,502
Truth is not on the battlefield.

136
00:09:44,839 --> 00:09:46,007
It's late.

137
00:09:47,258 --> 00:09:49,010
Good night, Clovis.

138
00:11:06,087 --> 00:11:09,423
Clovis, where are you going?

139
00:11:10,007 --> 00:11:12,009
I have some business to attend to.

140
00:11:12,093 --> 00:11:14,637
This was your idea.

141
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:18,432
I should very much like for you
to await the Senator's return.

142
00:11:31,737 --> 00:11:33,364
If you'll follow me,

143
00:11:33,447 --> 00:11:36,659
the credits for the Republic
are in this section.

144
00:12:44,185 --> 00:12:45,603
What happened to the lights?

145
00:12:45,686 --> 00:12:47,563
I can't see a thing!

146
00:12:48,773 --> 00:12:52,068
Find out what is going on,
and open the vault immediately.

147
00:12:52,151 --> 00:12:55,279
Power has been cut,
and the security lock has engaged.

148
00:12:55,363 --> 00:12:57,198
It will take some time to switch over.

149
00:13:27,728 --> 00:13:31,023
-Where is the Senator?
-We got separated in the darkness.

150
00:13:31,107 --> 00:13:32,274
I'm here.

151
00:13:32,358 --> 00:13:34,443
No thanks to your security system.

152
00:13:34,527 --> 00:13:37,947
This isn't a vault. It's a tomb.
What is going on?

153
00:13:38,406 --> 00:13:41,158
My deepest apologies, Senator.

154
00:13:41,242 --> 00:13:44,412
It seems I'm witness
to many firsts on Scipio.

155
00:13:44,495 --> 00:13:47,540
Is this an unfortunate incident
or a cover up?

156
00:13:47,748 --> 00:13:50,501
I'm not sure what you mean.

157
00:13:50,876 --> 00:13:53,713
I'm afraid I'm going to have to report
on your sad state of affairs

158
00:13:53,796 --> 00:13:55,131
to the Chancellor.

159
00:14:09,228 --> 00:14:11,522
Let's see if you got what we needed.

160
00:14:21,115 --> 00:14:24,035
As I said, the vaults are empty.

161
00:14:24,118 --> 00:14:26,954
The Chancellor
must see this immediately.

162
00:14:29,957 --> 00:14:33,377
Senator Amidala,
you are under arrest for espionage.

163
00:14:33,461 --> 00:14:35,629
No, there's been some kind of mistake.

164
00:14:36,130 --> 00:14:37,715
Take her away.

165
00:14:45,723 --> 00:14:49,060
I have powerful friends.
The Chancellor will hear about this.

166
00:15:08,788 --> 00:15:11,373
This way, Master Jedi.

167
00:15:16,837 --> 00:15:20,591
Well, well, well.
What exactly is going on here?

168
00:15:20,674 --> 00:15:23,844
Ani. I'm so glad to see you.

169
00:15:25,096 --> 00:15:27,807
I guess I'm not only useful
for fighting wars after all.

170
00:15:28,182 --> 00:15:31,602
-How long have I been in here?
-A few days.

171
00:15:31,685 --> 00:15:34,355
They say Teckla is dead. Is it true?

172
00:15:35,356 --> 00:15:37,858
Yes. She was found shot
at the bombsite.

173
00:15:38,275 --> 00:15:40,319
-By who?
-They don't know.

174
00:15:40,402 --> 00:15:43,072
The Muuns say
she sabotaged the power grid.

175
00:15:43,155 --> 00:15:45,199
What exactly is going on here?

176
00:15:45,282 --> 00:15:47,076
You have to get me out of here.

177
00:15:47,159 --> 00:15:49,245
-Clovis is...
-Clovis?

178
00:15:49,995 --> 00:15:52,289
What exactly does Clovis
have to do with this?

179
00:15:53,874 --> 00:15:55,376
I can't explain it here.

180
00:15:55,459 --> 00:15:59,964
How could you ever put your trust
in a man like Clovis after what he did?

181
00:16:00,047 --> 00:16:02,091
It's for the Republic, Anakin.

182
00:16:02,174 --> 00:16:04,885
Something is very wrong
with the banks.

183
00:16:05,094 --> 00:16:06,929
Why is it that when Clovis is around,

184
00:16:07,012 --> 00:16:10,683
your excuse is always that
you're doing it for the Republic?

185
00:16:12,059 --> 00:16:13,727
Anakin, please.

186
00:16:14,353 --> 00:16:16,397
You know, maybe
I'll just leave you here.

187
00:16:16,730 --> 00:16:18,107
Ani.

188
00:16:18,691 --> 00:16:20,651
You've already been released
into my custody.

189
00:16:20,734 --> 00:16:23,779
You better come with me
before I change my mind.

190
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:34,707
Anakin, please trust me.

191
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:38,335
I can't leave without the files
Clovis and I took from the vault.

192
00:16:38,419 --> 00:16:40,713
Where exactly do you suggest we look?

193
00:16:41,005 --> 00:16:45,009
The disks may be outside the city
at Clovis' private residence.

194
00:16:45,676 --> 00:16:49,889
Fine. I'll do this for you,
not for Clovis. Artoo.

195
00:16:51,515 --> 00:16:53,475
Have the ship ready in case I need you.

196
00:17:07,781 --> 00:17:09,491
Over there.

197
00:17:29,887 --> 00:17:31,263
Cozy place.

198
00:17:31,847 --> 00:17:35,601
Someone was looking for the files.
They must know Clovis has them.

199
00:17:35,684 --> 00:17:37,561
Well, maybe they found
what they were looking for,

200
00:17:37,645 --> 00:17:39,897
and that's why he's missing.

201
00:17:39,980 --> 00:17:41,065
We can only hope.

202
00:17:41,148 --> 00:17:43,359
Anakin, you're not helping things.

203
00:17:43,442 --> 00:17:46,111
You don't seem to understand
how important these files are.

204
00:17:46,403 --> 00:17:51,075
They'll expose a corruption that goes
to the very core of the Banking Clan.

205
00:17:51,158 --> 00:17:52,326
Clovis!

206
00:17:53,577 --> 00:17:54,995
Padmé.

207
00:17:55,788 --> 00:17:56,872
I knew you'd come.

208
00:17:59,875 --> 00:18:01,168
You again?

209
00:18:01,543 --> 00:18:03,879
Yes, me again.

210
00:18:03,963 --> 00:18:06,590
All right, lover boy, where's the disk?

211
00:18:06,674 --> 00:18:09,969
I'm not about to hand over
the information to some pilot.

212
00:18:10,052 --> 00:18:14,098
I'm a Jedi Knight who can save your life
if you hand over the files!

213
00:18:14,181 --> 00:18:18,018
So, what's it going to be?
You gonna give us the disk?

214
00:18:18,102 --> 00:18:20,938
Why? So you can leave me stranded
like last time?

215
00:18:21,021 --> 00:18:23,524
Well, that depends on
how well-behaved you are.

216
00:18:23,607 --> 00:18:27,069
Can you both stop bickering
so we can get out of here?

217
00:18:36,245 --> 00:18:37,538
Down!

218
00:18:40,874 --> 00:18:41,875
Thanks.

219
00:18:41,959 --> 00:18:43,961
It wasn't you I wanted to save.

220
00:18:44,044 --> 00:18:46,005
Anakin, get us out of here.

221
00:18:46,088 --> 00:18:47,256
Follow me!

222
00:18:48,549 --> 00:18:50,050
Run for it!

223
00:19:23,375 --> 00:19:26,045
Artoo, bring the ship around
and pick us up.

224
00:20:06,168 --> 00:20:07,169
Look out!

225
00:20:08,128 --> 00:20:09,421
Anakin!

226
00:20:19,139 --> 00:20:20,474
Did we lose him?

227
00:20:27,106 --> 00:20:28,107
I'm all right.

228
00:20:39,326 --> 00:20:42,329
Artoo, hone in on my signal. Artoo?

229
00:20:50,796 --> 00:20:52,131
Hey, nice catch.

230
00:21:18,031 --> 00:21:22,035
<i>It seems your mission was a success,
bounty hunter.</i>

231
00:21:22,119 --> 00:21:26,039
<i>From this point,
I will deal with them myself.</i>

232
00:21:26,063 --> 00:21:31,063
http://hiqve.com/

